transformations.description: This source is a Insured query using a union. The first portion of the query will use the additional_interest_stg, basicpolicy_stg, plicy_risk_key_reference and application_stg tables. The second portion of the query will use the additional_interest_application_stg, basicpolicyapp_stg, policy_risk_key_reference and application_stg tables.
transformations.name: src_query

object.customQuery:
select
	distinct 
        prkr.policy_system_id as policy_system_id,
	prkr.policy_number as policy_number,
	prkr.policy_module_number as policy_module_number,
	prkr.policy_key as policy_key,
	ai.systemid as additional_interest_system_id,
	ai.parentid as additional_interest_parent_id,
	ai.cmmcontainer as additional_interest_cmm_container,
	ai.id as additional_interest_id,
	ai.interesttypecd as additional_interest_type_code,
	ai.accountnumber as additional_interest_account_number,
	ai.interestname as additional_interest_name,
	ai.sequencenumber as additional_interest_sequence_number,
	ai.status as additional_interest_status,
	t.uw_dashboard_additional_insured_details_row_id,
	t.uw_dashboard_additional_insured_details_md5_hash_value
from
	dbo.additional_interest_stg ai
left join dbo.basicpolicy_stg bs 
on
	ai.parentid = bs.parentid
	and ai.systemid = bs.systemid
	and ai.cmmcontainer = bs.cmmcontainer
left join dbo.policy_risk_key_reference prkr
on
	bs.systemid = prkr.policy_system_id
	and bs.cmmcontainer = prkr.policy_cmm_container
	and bs.id = prkr.policy_reference_id
left join dbo.uw_dashboard_additional_insured_details t
on
	ai.systemid = t.additional_interest_system_id
	and ai.id = t.additional_interest_id
	and ai.cmmcontainer = t.additional_interest_cmm_container
	and t.uw_dashboard_additional_insured_details_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31'
where ai.status = 'Active'
  and prkr.policy_risk_key_reference_row_effective_end_date = '9999-12-31'
union
select
	distinct 
	prkr.policy_system_id,
	prkr.policy_number,
	prkr.policy_module_number,
	prkr.policy_key,
	ai.additional_interest_system_id,
	ai.additional_interest_parent_id,
	ai.additional_interest_cmm_container,
	ai.additional_interest_id,
	ai.additional_interest_type_code,
	ai.additional_interest_account_number,
	ai.additional_interest_name,
	ai.additional_interest_sequence_number,
	ai.additional_interest_status,
	t.uw_dashboard_additional_insured_details_row_id,
	t.uw_dashboard_additional_insured_details_md5_hash_value
from
	dbo.additional_interest_application_stg ai
left join dbo.basicpolicyapp_stg bs
on
	ai.additional_interest_parent_id = bs.parentid
	and ai.additional_interest_system_id = bs.systemid
	and ai.additional_interest_cmm_container = bs.cmmcontainer
left join dbo.policy_risk_key_reference prkr
on
	ai.additional_interest_system_id = prkr.policy_system_id
	and ai.additional_interest_cmm_container = prkr.policy_cmm_container
left join dbo.uw_dashboard_additional_insured_details t
on
	ai.additional_interest_system_id = t.additional_interest_system_id
	and ai.additional_interest_id = t.additional_interest_id
	and ai.additional_interest_cmm_container = t.additional_interest_cmm_container
	and t.uw_dashboard_additional_insured_details_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31'
where ai.additional_interest_status = 'Active'
  and prkr.policy_risk_key_reference_row_effective_end_date = '9999-12-31'
